  <name>System Monitor</name>
  <summary>Elegant system monitoring dashboard for Linux</summary>
  
  <description>
    <p>
      System Monitor by @efracode is a beautiful and modern system monitoring dashboard
      for Linux that displays real-time information about your system performance.
    </p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Real-time CPU usage per core with animated charts</li>
      <li>Memory (RAM and Swap) statistics with detailed breakdown</li>
      <li>Network speed monitoring (download/upload)</li>
      <li>Disk usage and partition information</li>
      <li>System temperature monitoring</li>
      <li>Floating desktop widgets for CPU, RAM, and Network</li>
      <li>Professional light mode design</li>
      <li>Always-on-top mode for continuous monitoring</li>
      <li>Updates every second for accurate real-time data</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
  
  <launchable type="desktop-id">com.efracode.systemmonitor.desktop</launchable>
  
